  "name": "Reaving Strike",
  "type": "feat",
  "img": "modules/pf1spheres/assets/icons/spheres/fencing.webp",
  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Prerequisites:</strong> Fencing sphere, base attack bonus +5.</p>\n<p>As long as you have martial focus, when you strike an opponent that has a chance of negating critical hits or precision damage, such as from the fortification armor special ability, reduce that chance by 5% per point of base attack bonus you possess.</p>\n<p>When you use this effect, you may expend martial focus to treat creatures that are normally immune to critical hits and precision damage as having a 150% chance to negate the critical hit or precision damage, reduced as normal by this talent&#8217;s effect. Treat creatures with a 100% fortification chance or greater as if they were immune to critical hits and precision damage (thus having an effective 150% chance to negate such effects) for the purposes of this talent. <strong>Associated Feat:</strong> Anatomical Savant.</p>\n",
